data.title: FOX 5 Atlanta, WAGA-TV
data.meta_description: FOX 5 Atlanta, WAGA-TV | 3,037 followers on LinkedIn. We are the FOX affiliate television station serving the Atlanta, GA market. FOX 5 News produces more local news than any other station in Atlanta. Our news products include Good Day Atlanta (4:30 - 11am), FOX 5 News at Noon, FOX 5 News at 4pm, 5pm & 6pm, FOX 5 News at 10pm, and FOX 5 News Edge at 11pm.
